property.name: outlif_physical_phase_data_granularity
property.doc: Assign a data granularity to each outlif physical phase. The suffix for this property is the physical phase, and the value is the data granularity. Valid data granularity values are 30/60/120 bits. Every physical phase must be configured. See related soc property outlif_logical_to_physical_phase_map. outlif_physical_phase_data_granularity_<Type>=<30|60|120> Default: 60.
